{"title":"荐歌：留守者（崔健）","slug":"荐歌：留守者（崔健）","date":"2022-05-27T10:29:39.000Z","updated":"2022-05-27T10:32:56.405Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/荐歌：留守者（崔健）.json","excerpt":"文章来自微信公众号“科文路”，欢迎关注、互动。转发须注明出处。周末愉快！今日推荐《留守者》，来自崔健。“留守者的反义词是出走者、叛逃者。农村里的年轻人都走了，就剩下一些老人、孩子、妇女。所以国内现在叫留守者。我一方面想起了他们，一方面想起了那些出走者（出国的人）。”<br>","covers":null,"content":"<blockquote>\n<p>文章来自微信公众号“科文路”，欢迎关注、互动。转发须注明出处。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>周末愉快！今日推荐《留守者》，来自崔健。</p>\n<p>“留守者的反义词是出走者、叛逃者。农村里的年轻人都走了，就剩下一些老人、孩子、妇女。所以国内现在叫留守者。我一方面想起了他们，一方面想起了那些出走者（出国的人）。”<br><span id=\"more\"></span></p>\n<p>以上是崔健对于《留守者》这首歌的引子。</p>\n<p>没啥好多说的，好听就完事儿了~摇滚不死，摇滚甚至不老~</p>\n<p>谁说现在没有好音乐了？这不就是？</p>\n<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=y3243qjmodk\" allowFullScreen=\"true\"></iframe>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</span><br><span class=\"line\">44</span><br><span class=\"line\">45</span><br><span class=\"line\">46</span><br><span class=\"line\">47</span><br><span class=\"line\">48</span><br><span class=\"line\">49</span><br><span class=\"line\">50</span><br><span class=\"line\">51</span><br><span class=\"line\">52</span><br><span class=\"line\">53</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">你说你要走</span><br><span class=\"line\">我并没有挽留</span><br><span class=\"line\">而且我还抬着头</span><br><span class=\"line\">泪水在口中流</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">你说走就走</span><br><span class=\"line\">还留下了一个借口</span><br><span class=\"line\">它像你的一只手</span><br><span class=\"line\">抓住我的</span><br><span class=\"line\">抓住我的心颤抖</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">你说你知道我</span><br><span class=\"line\">终将会变老</span><br><span class=\"line\">你说你知道我</span><br><span class=\"line\">会无所依靠</span><br><span class=\"line\">你说你知道我</span><br><span class=\"line\">在无声的喊叫</span><br><span class=\"line\">你却不知道</span><br><span class=\"line\">不知道</span><br><span class=\"line\">我已画地为牢</span><br><span class=\"line\">你说你要走</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">你要走就走</span><br><span class=\"line\">千万不要回头</span><br><span class=\"line\">因为你的借口</span><br><span class=\"line\">就是你的自由</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">我想吼却没吼</span><br><span class=\"line\">血气还是不够</span><br><span class=\"line\">我窒息着张着口</span><br><span class=\"line\">就像是一个</span><br><span class=\"line\">像是一个困兽</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">你说你知道我</span><br><span class=\"line\">终将会变老</span><br><span class=\"line\">你说你知道我<